## рҹҺ“ Best Practices Summary

### Do's вң…

- вң… Always include tenantId in queries
- вң… Use service layer for business logic
- вң… Validate all inputs with Zod
- вң… Log important operations
- вң… Use async/await consistently
- вң… Handle errors gracefully
- вң… Use TypeScript strictly
- вң… Write tests for critical paths
- вң… Use connection pooling
- вң… Cache frequently accessed data

### Don'ts вқҢ

- вқҢ Don't query without tenant filter
- вқҢ Don't put business logic in routes
- вқҢ Don't skip input validation
- вқҢ Don't ignore errors
- вқҢ Don't use var (use const/let)
- вқҢ Don't make synchronous calls in loops
- вқҢ Don't store secrets in code
- вқҢ Don't skip type checking
- вқҢ Don't create N+1 queries
- вқҢ Don't ignore performance warnings

